'''1862年大西洋飓风季'''共形成六个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，其中只有一个曾经[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。全季共有三个气旋达到热带风暴标准，三个达到飓风强度，没有[[热带气旋等级|大型飓风]]{{#tag:ref|大型飓风是指强度在现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下可以达到三级或以上标准的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]<ref>{{cite book | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/tcfaqHED.html | title = Hurricane Research Division: Frequently Asked Questions | chapter = A: Basic Definitions | chapterurl = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/tcfaqA.html | archivedate = 2016-05-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160510023152/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/tcfaqA.html | deadurl = no | at = [http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/A3.html A3) What is a super-typhoon? What is a major hurricane ? What is an intense hurricane ?] | author1 = Christopher W. Landsea | author2 = Neal Dorst | publisher = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | date = 2011-06-02 | accessdate = 2016-11-24 }}</ref>。|group="注"}}。不过，考虑到当时缺乏包括气象卫星在内的现代观测手段，基本上只有那些在海上遇到船只或是吹袭有人类居住陆地的风暴才有文献记载，所以实际形成的热带气旋可能更多。[[气象学|气象学家]][[克里斯托弗·朗诗|克里斯托弗·朗诗]]（{{lang|en|Christopher W. Landsea}}）估计，1851至1885年间实际形成的风暴数量可能比数据库中要多零到六场。<ref>{{cite book | title = Hurricanes and Typhoons: Past, Present and Future | chapter = The Atlantic hurricane database re-analysis project: Documentation for the 1851–1910 alterations and additions to the HURDAT database | author = Christopher W. Landsea | year = 2004 | publisher = Columbia University Press | isbn = 0-231-12388-4 | pages = 177–221}}</ref>全季确认存在的六个北大西洋热带气旋中有五个是由[[气象学|气象学家]]何塞·费尔南德斯-帕塔加斯（{{lang|en|Jose Fernandez-Partagas}}）和亨利·迪亚兹（{{lang|en|Henry Diaz}}）在1995年出版的文献中首度记载，另一个则是2003年迈克尔·切诺维斯（{{lang|en|Michael Chenoweth}}）根据[[巴拿马|巴拿马]][[科隆_(巴拿马)|科隆]]的纪录加入。

6月15至17日，本季首场热带风暴出现在[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]近海。第二场则要到约两个月后的8月中旬才形成，第三个气旋又要到9月中旬成型，两场风暴的最高强度都能在现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下达到二级飓风标准{{#tag:ref|[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]于1971年面世<ref name="USA Today">{{cite news | author = Jack Williams | title = Hurricane scale invented to communicate storm danger | publisher = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | date = 2005-05-17 | accessdate = 2013-08-04 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324154907/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-24 }}</ref>，再对[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]大西洋飓风数据库的所有风暴追溯分级<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Hurricane Research Division | title = Chronological List of All Continental United States Hurricanes: 1851-2012 | date = 2013-06 | accessdate = 2016-11-10 | archivedate = 2016-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160503012801/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html }}</ref>。|group="注"}}，但均未登陆。10月5日，第四个热带气旋在[[圣卢西亚|圣卢西亚]]引发洪灾，又在[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]部分地区降下暴雨，但风暴此前的发展历程已不可考。第五号飓风确定曾于10月在美国东岸近海活动，第六个气旋的中心于11月22至25日间在巴拿马附近活动。

这年飓风季低迷的活跃程度还经累积[[气旋能量指数|气旋能量指数]]反映出来，数值仅有46<ref name="ACE">{{cite report | author = Hurricane Research Division | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2011-03 | title = Atlantic basin Comparison of Original and Revised HURDAT | accessdate = 2016-03-04 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040342/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/Comparison_of_Original_and_Revised_HURDAT_mar11.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/Comparison_of_Original_and_Revised_HURDAT_mar11.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。大致来说，气旋能量指数通过飓风强度和持续时间计算，强度越高、持续时间越长的风暴，其指数也相应越高。只有在热带天气系统风速达到或超过每小时63公里（34[[节_(单位)|节]]）或热带风暴强度时才会计算该指数，并纳入全面的气象公告，并且[[亚热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]的指数不会计入累积数值。<ref>{{cite web |author=David Levinson |date=2008-08-20 |title=2005 Atlantic Ocean Tropical Cyclones |publisher=National Climatic Data Center |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20131105020723/http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2005/2005-atlantic-trop-cyclones.html |archivedate=2013-11-05 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2014-04-01 |url=http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2005/2005-atlantic-trop-cyclones.html }}</ref>
