气象机构根据四艘船只的报告推断，6月中旬[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]近海有热带风暴存在并持续两天<ref name="partagas-1">{{cite book | author1 = Jose Fernández-Partagás | author2 = Henry F. Diaz | title = A Reconstruction of Historical Tropical Cyclone Frequency in the Atlantic from Documentary and other Historical Sources 1851-1880 Part 1: 1851-1870 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/part1.htm | publisher = Climate Diagnostics Center, National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304204604/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/part1.htm | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | location = Boulder, Colorado | year = 1995 | accessdate = 2016-11-25 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。气旋于6月15日在[[萨凡纳|萨凡纳]]以东约550公里海域形成，然后缓慢北上，于两天后在[[弗吉尼亚海滩|弗吉尼亚海滩]]以东约400公里洋面逐渐消散<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] }}</ref>。
